{"tid":2490003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍又在渤海軍演　發布16日至18日禁航警告","createTime":"2021-04-15T09:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:13:16.000Z","uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37ee0d7dd25c9468f41bb176d150b18a5b3dd6db","tid":2490003,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"中國大連海事局周四（15日）發布航行警告，將於4月16日至18日，每天0900時至1700時，在渤海執行軍事任務。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國海事局官網公布，大連海事局15日發布「遼航警0056」航行警告，宣布4月16日至18日，每天0900時至1700時，在渤海執行軍事任務。<br />\n<br />\n公布指，禁航範圍為以北緯39&deg;50&prime;48&Prime;東經121&deg;10&prime;02&Prime;為中心，半徑8公里的海域內執行軍事任務，要求無關船舶禁止駛入。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍近來頻繁發布黃海、渤海軍演消息。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月，中國大連海事局也發布航行警告，指稱21日至28日在渤海海峽、黃海北部的部份海域將有軍事任務，禁止駛入。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡《聯合早報》報導曾指，一般認為，解放軍高調宣告演習，是因應近期美國海軍航艦也頻繁進出台灣海峽、南海海域航行，較勁意味濃厚。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"b632ca97af5febc023f134c810b686909fee2aad","tid":2490003,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210415/XBUP2FY6ARAQ3P33OXUTL3LVLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210415%2FXBUP2FY6ARAQ3P33OXUTL3LVLE%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=20154884\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210415%2FXBUP2FY6ARAQ3P33OXUTL3LVLE%2F&h=46c966bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210415/XBUP2FY6ARAQ3P33OXUTL3LVLE/</a>"},{"pid":"c48c8c0efdc1f9dc2cbbdd5035419baf388fa3dc","tid":2490003,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425182797293829e7864bb6107478144e800f94a","tid":2490003,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXrN5DNda56cSAjEXtmjjQk5J7J